Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of machine learning methods, specifically reinforcement learning, for traffic signal control. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the coordination of movements at road intersections, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of advanced methods to drive the development of intelligent transportation, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
